SUMMARY:Upstream: Digital Tech Meetup at Second Draught
DTSTAMP:20260701T101457Z
DTSTART:20260709T173000Z
DESCRIPTION:Register here: https://luma.com/timbergrove \nUpstream: Digital
	 Tech Meetup – Monthly Social 🍻 \nNo stage. No slides. No panels. \nJust u
	pstream operators\, engineers\, founders\, and digital leaders getting tog
	ether over beer and pizza. \nThis is the informal side of the Upstream Dig
	ital Tech community. A casual\, vendor-light happy hour for people navigat
	ing digital change in oil and gas and wanting real conversations. \nIt’s n
	ot a presentation. It’s not a pitch night.\nIt’s a room full of people who
	 are actually doing the work. \nA place to: \n• Meet others working at the
	 intersection of upstream and technology\n• Trade field stories\, lessons 
	learned\, and hard truths\n• Talk AI\, IoT\, data\, automation\, and deplo
	yment realities\n• Build real relationships without a formal agenda \nWhet
	her you’re deploying technology\, evaluating it\, building it\, or leading
	 teams through it\, you’ll fit right in. \nCome as you are.\nBring a frien
	d.\nStay as long as you like. \n📍 Second Draught @ The Ion District\, Midt
	own Houston\n🗓️ Second Thursday of every month | ⏰ 5:30 PM \n👉 Reserve your
	 spot. Space is limited.\n\nhttps://iondistrict.com/event/upstream-digital
	-tech-meetup-at-second-draught-3/2026-07-09/\n\nFrom Ion District
URL:https://iondistrict.com/event/upstream-digital-tech-meetup-at-second-dr
	aught-3/2026-07-09/
LOCATION:Second Draught\, 4201 Main St. Suite 130\, Houston\, TX\, 77002\, 
	United States
